<div class="policy-page">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="policy-title">Shipping &amp; Returns</h1>

    <div class="policy-section">
      <h2 class="policy-heading">Shipping</h2>
      <p class="policy-para">We offer free standard shipping on all orders to Canada and the United States. No minimum order required.</p>

      <div class="policy-table">
        <div class="policy-table-row policy-table-header">
          <span>Region</span>
          <span>Carrier</span>
          <span>Estimated Delivery</span>
        </div>
        <div class="policy-table-row">
          <span>Canada</span>
          <span>Canada Post</span>
          <span>5 to 8 business days</span>
        </div>
        <div class="policy-table-row">
          <span>United States</span>
          <span>USPS / Canada Post</span>
          <span>7 to 12 business days</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="policy-para">Orders are processed within 1 to 2 business days of being placed. You will receive a tracking number by email once your order ships. Delivery timelines are estimates and may vary during peak periods.</p>
      <p class="policy-para">We do not currently ship outside of Canada and the United States. If you are located elsewhere, email us at <a href="mailto:Lalumecare@gmail.com">Lalumecare@gmail.com</a> and we will do our best to help.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-section">
      <h2 class="policy-heading">30-Day Money-Back Guarantee</h2>
      <p class="policy-para">If you are not visibly happier with your skin within 30 days of receiving your order, we will refund you in full. No receipt required. No product return required. No questions asked.</p>
      <p class="policy-para">To request a refund, email us at <a href="mailto:Lalumecare@gmail.com">Lalumecare@gmail.com</a> with your order number and we will process the refund within 3 to 5 business days.</p>
      <p class="policy-para">Refunds are issued to the original payment method. If you paid via Shop Pay installments, refunds are applied to your outstanding balance first.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-section">
      <h2 class="policy-heading">Damaged or Incorrect Orders</h2>
      <p class="policy-para">If your order arrives damaged or you received the wrong item, contact us at <a href="mailto:Lalumecare@gmail.com">Lalumecare@gmail.com</a> within 7 days of delivery. Include your order number and a photo and we will send a replacement at no cost.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-section">
      <h2 class="policy-heading">Questions</h2>
      <p class="policy-para">For anything not covered here, email us at <a href="mailto:Lalumecare@gmail.com">Lalumecare@gmail.com</a>. We reply within 24 hours on business days.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
